1
00:00:03,060 --> 00:00:10,170
Today is a very important day in our lives as Sahaja yogis.

2
00:00:12,040 --> 00:00:15,230
This is the day when Sahasrara was opened out,

3
00:00:17,030 --> 00:00:22,210
which was really a very charismatic thing that happened.

4
00:00:25,010 --> 00:00:26,210
I never expected

5
00:00:27,230 --> 00:00:31,030
that in My lifetime I’ll be able to work it out,

6
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:33,170
but it has been,

7
00:00:34,010 --> 00:00:39,090
and so many of you have got your Sahasrara opened.

8
00:00:42,030 --> 00:00:45,040
Without that you could never have known

9
00:00:45,200 --> 00:00:47,150
what is the truth.

10
00:00:49,090 --> 00:00:53,030
You were all lost, as everybody is.

11
00:00:56,040 --> 00:00:58,000
First of all,

12
00:00:58,120 --> 00:01:04,010
Sahasrara is the only way we can perceive,

13
00:01:04,210 --> 00:01:09,230
understand and know the reality.

14
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:15,210
You have come to know

15
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:19,200
as to what is the reality,

16
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:24,180
and you are enjoying that state

17
00:01:25,100 --> 00:01:30,180
where you know what is the reality.

18
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:40,040
It’s a great blessing that Sahasrara was opened out

19
00:01:41,010 --> 00:01:44,100
and all of you got your realization.

20
00:01:45,150 --> 00:01:48,100
Otherwise all talks are just talks

21
00:01:49,010 --> 00:01:50,210
– has no meaning,

22
00:01:51,030 --> 00:01:53,030
has no understanding;

23
00:01:53,120 --> 00:02:00,010
and that’s why My first anxiety was to open Sahasrara.

24
00:02:00,170 --> 00:02:02,100
That worked out,

25
00:02:03,010 --> 00:02:04,210
worked out well,

26
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:07,060
and all of you have got

27
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:10,040
your Sahasrara opened.

28
00:02:10,150 --> 00:02:12,140
It’s a remarkable thing.

29
00:02:13,030 --> 00:02:17,090
Nobody can believe that so many of you have got

30
00:02:18,010 --> 00:02:23,040
your Sahasrara open, but I can see now clearly

31
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:25,230
the light on top of your heads.

32
00:02:27,230 --> 00:02:32,010
Whatever you have achieved is remarkable, no doubt.

33
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:36,010
It is because of honest searching,

34
00:02:36,230 --> 00:02:38,150
honest searching,

35
00:02:39,090 --> 00:02:41,060
that you have got it.

36
00:02:41,230 --> 00:02:44,000
My doing is nothing,

37
00:02:44,110 --> 00:02:46,220
because you were just there

38
00:02:47,060 --> 00:02:52,040
like a lamp and I just enlightened it, that’s all.

39
00:02:53,030 --> 00:02:55,040
It’s not such a big thing to do,

40
00:02:56,000 --> 00:03:00,150
as you people have achieved your state,

41
00:03:02,140 --> 00:03:05,050
state of enlightenment,

42
00:03:05,130 --> 00:03:07,220
that you got it because

43
00:03:08,140 --> 00:03:11,110
you were hankering after it,

44
00:03:11,220 --> 00:03:13,210
working it out,

45
00:03:14,130 --> 00:03:16,070
and you did it.

46
00:03:16,170 --> 00:03:18,220
It’s very creditable.

47
00:03:19,130 --> 00:03:21,160
Credit doesn’t go to Me, I think,

48
00:03:21,210 --> 00:03:24,080
because I had a open Sahasrara,

49
00:03:25,050 --> 00:03:27,220
but to achieve that in you people

50
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:32,210
was so joy-giving for Me.

51
00:03:33,190 --> 00:03:36,080
Now you will understand,

52
00:03:36,220 --> 00:03:40,140
because if Sahasrara is not open you can’t talk people,

53
00:03:40,220 --> 00:03:43,030
you can’t say anything to them

54
00:03:43,110 --> 00:03:45,190
– it’s just they don’t understand.

55
00:03:47,060 --> 00:03:51,240
With the Sahasrara open your understanding improves so much.

56
00:03:52,110 --> 00:03:55,110
That is what has happened with all of you,

57
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:57,240
and I’m so very happy

58
00:03:58,080 --> 00:04:01,110
that it’s so many people there are sitting here

59
00:04:01,220 --> 00:04:04,160
who have got their Sahasraras open.

60
00:04:04,220 --> 00:04:07,080
And there are many who have not come.

61
00:04:07,220 --> 00:04:12,220
So it’s a big achievement for human beings

62
00:04:13,190 --> 00:04:16,000
to get it so much collectively

63
00:04:17,030 --> 00:04:19,080
Sahasrara opened,

64
00:04:20,030 --> 00:04:24,080
by which you know the truth,

65
00:04:25,030 --> 00:04:27,020
absolute truth.

66
00:04:27,210 --> 00:04:31,030
Whatever you know after your realization

67
00:04:31,170 --> 00:04:33,140
is the absolute truth.

68
00:04:34,030 --> 00:04:35,240
You don’t argue then,

69
00:04:36,100 --> 00:04:37,220
don’t question,

70
00:04:38,130 --> 00:04:42,060
you just know it and you accept it

71
00:04:42,140 --> 00:04:44,100
as a knowledge.

72
00:04:44,180 --> 00:04:48,210
It’s such a nice thing that it was all there,

73
00:04:49,030 --> 00:04:51,010
but it was not open.

74
00:04:51,100 --> 00:04:55,240
And when it opened out, how people have understood Me

75
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:59,130
and also the laws of the Divine.

76
00:05:00,090 --> 00:05:02,200
It’s such a blessing of the Divine

77
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:06,230
that you have got your Sahasrara opened out,

78
00:05:07,100 --> 00:05:11,150
for which you may say, “We didn’t do anything, Mother.”

79
00:05:11,230 --> 00:05:13,100
It’s not so.

80
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:16,100
Your search for truth

81
00:05:16,180 --> 00:05:20,070
was intense and definite.

82
00:05:21,010 --> 00:05:23,100
You wanted to know the truth,

83
00:05:23,180 --> 00:05:25,180
that’s why it has worked out.

84
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:28,100
Otherwise no amount of money,

85
00:05:28,170 --> 00:05:30,040
no amount of effort,

86
00:05:30,070 --> 00:05:31,210
nothing would have helped.

87
00:05:32,150 --> 00:05:35,100
Sahasrara had to open by itself.

88
00:05:36,010 --> 00:05:40,150
It’s all your building up, I should say,

89
00:05:41,010 --> 00:05:45,060
it’s all your doing to yourself

90
00:05:45,130 --> 00:05:50,130
that has brought forth such a beautiful happening.

91
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:58,210
I do not take any credit for that at all.

92
00:05:59,100 --> 00:06:02,200
Definitely I must say

93
00:06:03,100 --> 00:06:05,130
that I have made you understand

94
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:10,070
that it’s important that your Sahasrara should be opened.

95
00:06:10,180 --> 00:06:12,150
No more arguments,

96
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:14,210
no more suggestions,

97
00:06:15,170 --> 00:06:19,130
nothing, but have your own Sahasrara open,

98
00:06:19,230 --> 00:06:22,150
which tells you what is the truth is.

99
00:06:23,150 --> 00:06:27,130
In these beautiful circumstances,

100
00:06:28,030 --> 00:06:30,120
what could your Mother say?

101
00:06:31,010 --> 00:06:37,030
I can only say that continue to live a life of reality,

102
00:06:37,070 --> 00:06:38,180
of understanding.

103
00:06:39,090 --> 00:06:41,140
In everything you will find

104
00:06:41,210 --> 00:06:43,090
there is truth,

105
00:06:43,200 --> 00:06:51,210
and how do we use that truth is our own achievement.

106
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:58,010
People are lost

107
00:06:58,150 --> 00:07:01,060
because they have no knowledge.

108
00:07:01,210 --> 00:07:05,120
Knowledge from the books is no knowledge.

109
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:08,200
Their knowledge must come from within,

110
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:11,050
from within themselves, you see,

111
00:07:11,110 --> 00:07:15,170
and that has happened because of Sahasrara opening.

112
00:07:16,170 --> 00:07:19,110
In all the countries it has happened,

113
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:22,110
and it will be in the whole world,

114
00:07:22,190 --> 00:07:25,160
so many people will get realization.

115
00:07:26,010 --> 00:07:30,200
But only thing I feel that you people should have

116
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:35,170
no emotional attachment to it,

117
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:40,240
not emotional but realistic attachment,

118
00:07:41,090 --> 00:07:46,060
that it is there, it has happened, it’s working out.

119
00:07:46,150 --> 00:07:50,170
Then you will be able to give realizations to other,

120
00:07:51,010 --> 00:07:54,100
you’ll understand the importance of realization.

121
00:07:55,010 --> 00:07:57,040
Unless and until you use it

122
00:07:57,120 --> 00:08:01,030
you won’t know what is the power of realization is.

123
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:05,090
So you must learn how to use this power

124
00:08:05,150 --> 00:08:06,230
which is within you,

125
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:09,070
which has started working out,

126
00:08:09,150 --> 00:08:13,140
and which will give you such a immense capacity.

127
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:22,140
My health is little bit gone down – after all, I am very old.

128
00:08:22,220 --> 00:08:27,110
But still I don’t feel tired in any way

129
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,100
while addressing you;

130
00:08:29,140 --> 00:08:32,030
I feel so enamored

131
00:08:32,130 --> 00:08:35,020
that there are so many Sahaja yogis,

132
00:08:35,060 --> 00:08:38,020
so many whose Sahasrara is opened,

133
00:08:38,060 --> 00:08:40,170
and they’re enjoying their Sahasrara.

134
00:08:41,050 --> 00:08:44,080
Actually I would have liked you to ask Me questions,

135
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:49,220
but you can write questions and send Me written ones.

136
00:08:50,050 --> 00:08:52,170
Then I’ll try to answer them some time.

137
00:08:53,020 --> 00:08:55,060
Will be a much better idea.

138
00:08:56,160 --> 00:08:58,140
So thank you very much.

139
00:08:58,220 --> 00:09:00,140
May God bless you.

140
00:09:01,050 --> 00:09:02,220
Grow into Sahaj,

141
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:06,000
grow into your being.

142
00:09:06,100 --> 00:09:10,050
May God bless you, all My blessings.

